episodes.title: Orb
episodes.plot: During the journey home from their sea-faring adventure; Finn, Jake, and BMO encounter a mysterious force that enters their dreams.

episodes.title: Elements Part 1: Skyhooks
episodes.plot: Finn, Jake, and BMO return from their voyage to a radically changed Ooo.

episodes.title: Elements Part 2: Bespoken For
episodes.plot: The friends learn the story of what happened to Ooo, while Betty continues her attempt to reach Simon, but she's interrupted by someone out to steal her magic.

episodes.title: Elements Part 3: Winter Light
episodes.plot: Finn, Jake and Ice King break into the Ice World to confront the power-hungry evildoer responsible for the chaos in Ooo and try to rescue Betty.

episodes.title: Elements Part 4: Cloudy
episodes.plot: After taking a nap, Finn and Jake get separated from Betty and the Ice King. They need to get back and Jake needs to go pee.

episodes.title: Elements Part 5: Slime Central
episodes.plot: In order to save Ooo, Finn and Jake must gather the four elemental gems. They go to the Slime Kingdom and have to gather Slime Princess's gem.

episodes.title: Elements Part 6: Happy Warrior
episodes.plot: After gathering the Slime jewel, Finn and LSP go to the Fire Kingdom, to gather the Flame Jewel. Everything has turned even hotter than before.

episodes.title: Elements Part 7: Hero Heart
episodes.plot: After going to the Fire Kingdom, Finn becomes taken over by fire. LSP has to save him before he destroys the candy kingdom.

episodes.title: Elements Part 8: Skyhooks II
episodes.plot: After saving Finn the human during a battle between the candy kingdom and the fire kingdom it is discovered that LSP is made of anti-elemental magic and restores Ooo to it's former state.

episodes.title: Abstract
episodes.plot: Jake struggles through the personal changes happening to him as a mysterious encounter in a dream with his brother Jermaine begins to haunt him.

episodes.title: Ketchup
episodes.plot: BMO and Marceline play catch up on recent events.

episodes.title: Fionna and Cake and Fionna
episodes.plot: While performing a reading of 'Fiona and Cake', Ice King is confronted by a familiar figure.

episodes.title: Whispers
episodes.plot: While safeguarding a frightened Sweet P, Finn is led into a confrontation with an old foe.

episodes.title: Three Buckets
episodes.plot: Finn and Fern's carefree visit to some old ruins turns disastrous.
